{"tid":360534,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★香港站信號故障　東涌綫及機場快綫行車時間受阻","createTime":"2017-08-15T11:09:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-16T07:51:42.000Z","uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e917c08d357c27f0e26978f2de59b74fcc0ef0c9","tid":360534,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:09:26.000Z","msg":"2017-08-15 HKT 18:55<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n港鐵表示，由於香港站有信號故障，東涌綫及機場快綫整體行車時間，延長10至15分鐘，呼籲前往機場的乘客預留時間，辦理登機手續。<br />\n<br />\n東涌綫往來香港站列車維持每8分鐘一班，機場快綫每15分鐘一班。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1348360-20170815.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1348360-20170815.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=CcDQHTJkwWMWMHuO2eWxe9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=1e8743d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1348360-20170815.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=99b7fbfb\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1348360-20170815.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"f0e1670610769ceaf08c52f55dac05629c69b141","tid":360534,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:09:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc954452f7e34f09e0b8c1e92db2d9e59742715a","tid":360534,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:10:23.000Z","msg":"好彩要OT"},{"pid":"80e312792eeebdef0cbb633daa7d3c60a2a74abb","tid":360534,"uid":31699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:10:37.000Z","msg":"屌又壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"371e93b508cdb8418a96b5f55c7fbb556bc8ef46","tid":360534,"uid":116530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:11:2